node.text:
We were fortunate enough to spend a weekend in Yokosuka, Japan entertaining the families living on the base there. We would like to thank the staff of the HMS Albion for their wonderful tour. 
Featuring Dakota Roche, Gary Young, Matthias Dandois, Josh Borden and Omar Hassan.

Video: Colin Mackay

node.text: Did you know, that both of these clips from @DennisEnarson’s “Right Here” (filmed in Colombia) he somehow managed to land only a couple of days after separating his shoulder? node.text: We want to congratulate @PatCaseyBMX on his Dirt gold medal + Park silver medal, and @KevinPeraza on his Park gold medal @XGames. That was Kevin’s 3rd gold! He only has gold medals from X Games! Also congrats and a shout out to @AndyBuckworth and @VansCanada’s @MikeVargaBMX their Best Trick wins yesterday and Mike’s Park bronze. X isn’t over yet! Street practice is today with the event going down on Friday night.
